item.title: I need help with my java
item.dc:creator: @mod_taharok Taharok
item.description:
@mod_taharok wrote:

[quote=“ephemeral, post:3, topic:173966”]RuneScape private server-related stuff goes at MoparScape.org (as probably is what he is referring to)… However, “server”-related stuff probably inherits to this Moparisthebest.com site.

My point is, it wouldn’t necessary have been a RuneScape private server he meant, by saying “server”. But of course, as this site used to be all about RuneScape private servers at first, that probably is a quite obvious sign that he is referring to private RuneScape servers.[/quote]

And because he said “make a private server.”
